“Towngas Fun” is a membership program, combined with online redemption platform, dedicatedly designed for our valuable customers by Towngas.

Towngas member entitles numerous privileges as below:
．Free membership – simply register online would do;
．Earn the points – every HKD$1 eligible spending would be reverted as 1 point, gas bill settlement would do as well;
．Redeem offers – points could be redeemed as special offers and participation in activities;
．Household account – household members could transfer points effortlessly;
．Upgrade privilege – reach the designated points, upgrade to enjoy more unique privilege.

DISCLAIMER: Apple is not a sponsor and is not involved in any way with the contests or sweepstakes mentioned in this app. Apple products are not offered as contest or sweepstake prizes.

